<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Hora - Password Reset OTP</title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 20px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f8fafc;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); overflow: hidden;">
        
        <!-- Header -->
        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); padding: 40px 30px; text-align: center; color: white;">
            <div style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; letter-spacing: -0.5px;">Hora</div>
            <div style="font-size: 14px; opacity: 0.9; font-weight: 300;">Time Tracking Made Simple</div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Content -->
        <div style="padding: 40px 30px;">
            <h1 style="color: #2d3748; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.3;">üîê Password Reset Request</h1>
            
            <p style="color: #718096; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px;">
                Hi <strong>{{user_name}}</strong>,
            </p>
            
            <p style="color: #718096; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px;">
                We received a request to reset your password for your Hora account. If you didn't make this request, you can safely ignore this email.
            </p>
            
            <!-- OTP Display -->
            <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); padding: 30px; border-radius: 12px; text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <h2 style="color: white; font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: 500;">Your Password Reset Code</h2>
                <div style="background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; display: inline-block;">
                    <div style="font-size: 36px; font-weight: 700; color: white; letter-spacing: 8px; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;">{{otp_code}}</div>
                </div>
                <p style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); font-size: 14px; margin-top: 15px;">
                    This code will expire in <strong>{{expiry_time}}</strong>
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Instructions -->
            <div style="background-color: #f8fafc; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
                <h3 style="color: #2d3748; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 18px;">üìã How to use this code:</h3>
                <ol style="color: #4a5568; line-height: 1.8; margin: 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                    <li>Go to the password reset page in your Hora app</li>
                    <li>Enter the 6-digit code above</li>
                    <li>Create a new strong password</li>
                    <li>Save your new password</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Security Notice -->
            <div style="background-color: #fff5f5; border: 1px solid #fed7d7; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
                <h3 style="color: #c53030; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 16px;">üîí Security Notice:</h3>
                <ul style="color: #c53030; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; font-size: 14px;">
                    <li>Never share this code with anyone</li>
                    <li>Hora staff will never ask for this code</li>
                    <li>If you didn't request this reset, contact support immediately</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Reset Button -->
            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="{{reset_url}}" style="display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 16px 32px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px;">
                    Reset My Password
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <p style="color: #718096; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px;">
                If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:
            </p>
            
            <p style="background-color: #f8fafc; padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 14px; color: #4a5568; word-break: break-all; margin: 20px 0;">
                {{reset_url}}
            </p>
            
            <p style="color: #718096; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px;">
                Need help? Contact our support team at <a href="mailto:{{support_email}}" style="color: #667eea;">{{support_email}}</a>
            </p>
            
            <p style="color: #718096; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px;">
                Thank you for using Hora!
            </p>
            
            <p style="color: #718096; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px;">
                Best regards,<br>
                <strong>The Hora Security Team</strong>
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Footer -->
        <div style="background-color: #2d3748; color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center;">
            <div style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 10px;">Hora</div>
            <p style="color: #a0aec0; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                Making time tracking simple and efficient for teams worldwide.
            </p>
            
            <div style="margin: 20px 0;">
                <a href="{{app_url}}" style="color: #a0aec0; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 15px; font-size: 14px;">Dashboard</a>
                <a href="{{help_url}}" style="color: #a0aec0; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 15px; font-size: 14px;">Help Center</a>
                <a href="{{contact_url}}" style="color: #a0aec0; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 15px; font-size: 14px;">Contact Us</a>
                <a href="{{privacy_url}}" style="color: #a0aec0; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 15px; font-size: 14px;">Privacy Policy</a>
            </div>
            
            <div style="margin-top: 20px;">
                <a href="{{twitter_url}}" style="display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: #4a5568; border-radius: 50%; margin: 0 5px; text-align: center; line-height: 40px; color: white; text-decoration: none; font-size: 18px;">ùïè</a>
                <a href="{{linkedin_url}}" style="display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: #4a5568; border-radius: 50%; margin: 0 5px; text-align: center; line-height: 40px; color: white; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold;">in</a>
                <a href="{{github_url}}" style="display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: #4a5568; border-radius: 50%; margin: 0 5px; text-align: center; line-height: 40px; color: white; text-decoration: none; font-size: 18px;">üêô</a>
            </div>
            
            <p style="color: #718096; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 20px;">
                ¬© 2024 Hora. All rights reserved.<br>
                {{company_address}}
            </p>
            
            <p style="color: #718096; font-size: 12px;">
                You're receiving this email because you requested a password reset for your Hora account.<br>
                <a href="{{unsubscribe_url}}" style="color: #a0aec0;">Unsubscribe</a> from these notifications.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
